OL,3,CThree charged over multi-million pound
OL,4,Cfraud at prestigious sixth form college
OL,6,FRagu Sivapalan, 39, from Penylan,
OL,7,FCardiff, has been charged with false
OL,8,Faccounting between 2013 and 2016.
OL,10,FAll three are expected to appear
OL,11,Fbefore Cardiff Magistrates Court on
OL,12,FTuesday, 8 April.
OL,14,FThe college, which is a fee-paying
OL,15,Fschool for 16 to 18-year-olds,
OL,16,Fregularly records some of the highest
OL,17,FA-level results in the country.
