OL,6,FA statement from Cardiff Educational
OL,7,FEndowment Trust said: "After the
OL,8,Falleged fraud, the college was sold by
OL,9,Fthe interim manager appointed by the
OL,10,FCharity Commission. The charity which
OL,11,Fformally owned the college changed its
OL,12,Fname to Cardiff Educational Endowment
OL,13,FTrust. Cardiff Educational Endowment
OL,14,FTrust is a grant-making charity and is
OL,15,Fnot involved in the governance or the
OL,16,Fmanagement of the college."
